summary: Hey everyone! As of today, i’ve officially re-launched my Patreon page. You can find it right here if you’d like to take a look...
caption:
Hey everyone!

As of today, i’ve officially re-launched my Patreon page. You can find it right here if you’d like to take a look and support me and my art.

Why am I on Patreon?

The support that will be given here on Patreon will be used to aid in my business and time to devote to art. It’s my dream that I can support myself someday in a manner that allows even more time than I have now to create new content beyond even my fan work. I have so many ideas I want to create and share with the world, but it becomes difficult when you have bills and living expenses that need to be considered first.

Why should you support me?

I hope that, in supporting me, you will find enjoyment from the content provided to you. I cannot thank those that help me enough for their interest in what I create both now and in the future. It’s in this, I want to give back to those that have followed me and have interest in my work.

Thank you so much for supporting me and my artwork!

summary:
Ok time for a story:
 When I first saw this illustration in Shaman King vol. 26 by my idol Hiroyuki Takei I thought it was the...
caption:
Ok time for a story:
When I first saw this illustration in Shaman King vol. 26 by my idol Hiroyuki Takei I thought it was the most amazing thing ever. I was 14 and the only thing I wished for was that someday I would be able to draw something like this. Today … out of nowhere … I thought about this single page, searched for the manga and started sketching it with a pen my mother left on the kitchen table. Over ten years later I sketched this while skyping with a friend. Without any problems or a lot of effort I created something I dreamed of for so long. I really wanna go back to my younger self and tell him: “Work hard and practise a lot and you will become even better then anything you wish for.” I’m kinda proud right now … 🖌✏❤
